
The following parameters can be set when calling the applet from
the command line.

-Dtablet.showancestor=[true|false]  default true
	list the ancestor node in the display or no

-Dtablet.allowautorun=[true|false]  default false
	allow automatic proving
	[switched off for didactic reasons]

-Dtablet.absolutetex=[true|false]  default ...
	position TeX export absolute or relative.

-Dtablet.fontsize=<number>  defualt 
	font size to be used to show nodes

-Dtablet.allowunification=[true|false]  default false
	allow the unification of formulas when drag'n'dropping
	nodes. [switched off for didactic reasons] 

